          Lux: %&DDAP*[0xFAFA]+0+[Lux Value]$[Somme des bits a 1 des champs du corps]@:@
          
      2nd type:
          acknowledge the reception
        
          Ack:  &%DDAP!:@:
          Nack: &%DDAP?:@:

    other quick test:

      header error: %&DAAP*#$13@:@
      footer error: %&DDAP*#$13
      damaged tram: %&DDAP*asdavhsdfgâ‚¬$13@:@
